item.description: 2020-06-26 Words Sentences make analysis difficult to impossible. counteract : 2020-06-25 Words thoroughly, entirely, completely, totally, fully, absolutely, strictly Sentences 2020-06-24 Words explicitly, specifically, definitely, particularly the blanketing effect of a growing H2O-CO2 atmosphere erase, delete, remove, eliminate, putative, supposed, assumed, presumptive Sentences The fundamental difference here is that instead of assuming the entire unstable compositional profile to be built before any solid-like mantle overturn can take place, we model its formation allowing for the possibility that solid-state convection sets in before the solidification front has reached the surface.
